org.ektorp.android.util

Class ChangesFeedAsyncTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Void,DocumentChange,Object>
      • org.ektorp.android.util.ChangesFeedAsyncTask

  • public abstract class ChangesFeedAsyncTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<Void,DocumentChange,Object>
    This class allows you to pull DocumentChanges off a CouchDB changes feed in the background and process them on the main thread.
